WEBVTT

00:03.337 --> 00:05.973
Daniel:
SO, I WENT FISHING THIS WEEKEND.

00:06.006 --> 00:08.176
CAUGHT A HUGE STRIPED BASS.

00:09.310 --> 00:10.978
THIS BIG.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.980
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:13.013 --> 00:14.148
WE'RE HAVING IT MOUNTED
IN MY OFFICE.

00:14.182 --> 00:15.316
ISN'T THAT RIGHT,
MR. LEWICKI?

00:15.349 --> 00:17.017
UH, WHATEVER
YOU SAY, DOC.

00:18.186 --> 00:19.220
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:22.022 --> 00:23.324
ALL RIGHT.

00:23.357 --> 00:25.993
SO, EVEN IF MY SOON-TO-BE
FORMER TEACHING ASSISTANT

00:26.026 --> 00:28.196
DIDN'T ROLL OVER ON ME
LIKE A RAT IN A BAD MAFIA FLICK,

00:28.229 --> 00:29.997
YOU'D KNOW I WAS LYING.

00:30.030 --> 00:30.998
WHY?

00:31.031 --> 00:32.300
'CAUSE IT'S A FISH STORY.

00:32.333 --> 00:38.005
BUT IF I WAS A BETTER LIAR,
I'D HAVE A HUGE ADVANTAGE.

00:38.038 --> 00:41.175
STUDIES SHOW THE MOST CONVINCING
LIARS LAND THE BEST JOBS,

00:41.209 --> 00:44.178
MAKE THE MOST FRIENDS,
AND GET ALL THE HOT WOMEN.

00:44.212 --> 00:46.214
SO IF I WAS REALLY GOOD AT IT,

00:46.247 --> 00:49.350
WOULD THERE STILL BE A WAY
FOR YOU TO BUST ME?

00:49.383 --> 00:51.319
A POLYGRAPH, MAYBE.

00:51.352 --> 00:53.020
[ BEEPING ]

00:53.053 --> 00:54.355
Kate: DID YOU DISCOVER
A MALE INTRUDER

00:54.388 --> 00:57.158
IN YOUR HOME LAST NIGHT?

00:57.191 --> 00:59.227
YES.

00:59.260 --> 01:02.029
DO YOU KNOW THE IDENTITY
OF THIS MAN?

01:02.062 --> 01:03.331
NO.

01:03.364 --> 01:05.099
DID YOU SEE HIS FACE?

01:05.133 --> 01:07.168
YES.

01:07.201 --> 01:09.237
CAN YOU DESCRIBE IT?

01:11.071 --> 01:12.340
NO.

01:14.108 --> 01:16.177
A POLYGRAPH'S
NOT A BAD TOOL,

01:16.210 --> 01:18.379
BUT IT ONLY MEASURES
STRESS RESPONSE.

01:18.412 --> 01:23.351
IN THIS CLASS, WE'RE INTERESTED
IN WHAT GOES ON IN THE BRAIN.

01:23.384 --> 01:26.254
AND IF WE WERE TO PUT SOMEONE
IN AN fMRI MACHINE

01:26.287 --> 01:29.190
AND WATCH WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN THEY MAKE UP A LIE,

01:29.223 --> 01:31.225
WE'D SEE THEIR DORSOLATERAL
PREFRONTAL CORTEX

01:31.259 --> 01:33.093
LIGHT UP
LIKE A CHRISTMAS TREE...

01:33.127 --> 01:34.262
[ LAUGHTER ]

01:34.295 --> 01:37.198
...BECAUSE WE USE OUR BRAINS
WHEN WE LIE.

01:37.231 --> 01:40.134
WE USE OUR BRAINS
WHEN WE'RE BEING LIED TO.

01:40.168 --> 01:42.136
BUT...

01:42.170 --> 01:47.175
CAN THE BRAIN
EVER LIE TO ITSELF?

01:53.113 --> 01:54.248
Max: ALL RIGHT.

01:54.282 --> 01:56.083
SO YOU'VE GOT OFFICE HOURS
FROM 1:00 TO 3:00,

01:56.116 --> 01:57.251
AND DON'T FORGET
THE MEETING

01:57.285 --> 01:59.119
WITH DEAN HALEY
AND THAT HATHAWAY GUY AT 4:00.

01:59.153 --> 02:00.388
GET OH, OKAY. IT.

02:00.421 --> 02:02.390
WHAT AM I
I DON'T KNOW.ELL HIM?

02:02.423 --> 02:04.425
USE YOUR DORSOLATERAL
PREFRONTAL CORTEX AND
MAKE SOMETHING UP.

02:04.458 --> 02:06.360
SO YOU WANT ME
TO LIE FOR YOU NOW?

02:06.394 --> 02:08.162
THINK OF IT AS FOR WHAT?

02:08.196 --> 02:10.097
FOR LANDING A NEW JOB
WHEN I FIRE YOU

02:10.130 --> 02:12.266
FOR NOT GETTING ME OUT
OF THE MEETING WITH DEAN HALEY.

02:12.300 --> 02:14.101
DOC, THAT DOESN'T
MAKE ANY SENSE.

02:14.134 --> 02:16.204
IT'S A PARADOX, LEWICKI.
IT'S NOT SUPPOSED TO.

02:18.339 --> 02:20.274
OH, GOD! I'M SO SORRY.

02:20.308 --> 02:22.443
[ British accent ]
IN A BIT OF A HURRY, AREN'T WE?

02:22.476 --> 02:24.412
I'M GONNA PAY FOR YOUR
DRY CLEANING, OKAY?

02:24.445 --> 02:26.447
MY FAULT. I WASN'T
LOOKING WHERE I WAS GOING.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.449
IN FACT, COULD WE PLEASE
MAKE THE LADY ANOTHER?

02:28.482 --> 02:31.118
I INSIST.FINE.

02:31.151 --> 02:33.254
[ SIGHS ]
CHAMOMILE TEA.

02:33.287 --> 02:34.388
GOOD CHOICE.

02:34.422 --> 02:36.290
I DON'T THINK YOU NEED
ANY MORE CAFFEINE.

02:36.324 --> 02:38.192
ACTUALLY,
THE TEA IS FOR A FRIEND,

02:38.226 --> 02:40.194
AND I CAN HANDLE MY CAFFEINE
JUST FINE.

02:40.228 --> 02:41.195
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

02:41.229 --> 02:42.396
HOW ABOUT YOUR LIQUOR?

02:42.430 --> 02:44.131
EXCUSE ME?

02:44.164 --> 02:45.333
WELL, SEEING AS I'M
BUYING THE TEA,

02:45.366 --> 02:47.335
I THOUGHT MAYBE
YOU COULD BUY ME A REAL DRINK.

02:47.368 --> 02:49.136
7:00's GOOD FOR ME.

02:49.169 --> 02:50.404
THANK YOU FOR THE TEA,

02:50.438 --> 02:54.375
AND AGAIN, I'M VERY SORRY
ABOUT THE SHIRT.

02:57.445 --> 03:00.147
Daniel: KATE.

03:00.180 --> 03:02.483
WHAT, AM I ON SOME SORT
OF GOVERNMENT WATCH LIST?

03:02.516 --> 03:04.184
NOT YET.

03:04.218 --> 03:06.487
HERBAL TEA.
NO MILK, NO SUGAR.

03:07.521 --> 03:10.491
NOW, I KNOW YOU DIDN'T
COME ALL THE WAY OVER HERE

03:10.524 --> 03:12.260
JUST TO BRING ME TEA.

03:14.194 --> 03:16.297
MEET FRANK
AND OLENA PRENTICE.

03:16.330 --> 03:17.465
LOOKS LIKE
HE WON THE LOTTERY.

03:17.498 --> 03:19.300
ACTUALLY,
SHE COST HIM A BUNDLE.

03:19.333 --> 03:20.468
MAIL-ORDER BRIDE
FROM THE UKRAINE.

03:20.501 --> 03:22.202
PEOPLE ACTUALLY
DO THAT?

03:22.236 --> 03:25.473
YEAH. WHY? ARE YOU
IN THE MARKET FOR A WIFE?

03:25.506 --> 03:27.207
NO.

03:28.242 --> 03:31.211
"EASTERN BLOC
INTRODUCTIONS."

03:31.245 --> 03:33.247
THEY ARRANGED FOR FRANK
TO FLY TO ODESSA

03:33.281 --> 03:35.182
TO MEET WITH
PROSPECTIVE BRIDES.

03:35.215 --> 03:37.385
BEFORE YOU KNOW IT,
WEDDING BELLS.

03:37.418 --> 03:41.455
BUT FRANK HAS TO COME HOME WHILE
THEY WAIT FOR OLENA'S VISA.

03:41.489 --> 03:43.257
IMMIGRATION PROBLEMS.

03:43.291 --> 03:44.458
THEN HE GETS A CALL
FROM HER BROKER

03:44.492 --> 03:46.360
SAYING IT'S GONNA BE
ANOTHER 100 GRAND

03:46.394 --> 03:47.561
TO GET OLENA
INTO THE STATES.

03:47.595 --> 03:50.197
NOW, FRANK DOESN'T HAVE
THAT KIND OF CASH.

03:50.230 --> 03:52.400
SO THEN THE BROKER OFFERS HIM
ALTERNATIVE FINANCING.

03:52.433 --> 03:54.402
CODE FOR "LOAN SHARK."

03:54.435 --> 03:55.503
EXACTLY.

03:55.536 --> 03:57.237
SO FRANK
GETS HIS NEW BRIDE,

03:57.271 --> 03:58.539
BUT HE CAN'T KEEP UP
WITH THE PAYMENTS.

03:58.572 --> 04:00.474
SO THEN THE LOAN SHARK
TELLS HIM

04:00.508 --> 04:03.511
THAT THEY'RE GOING
TO TAKE OLENA AND MAKE
HER WORK OFF THE DEBT.

04:03.544 --> 04:06.380
I'M GUESSING WE'RE NOT TALKING
ABOUT A NICE OFFICE JOB.

04:06.414 --> 04:08.215
[ CHUCKLES ]
ALEXEI TUPELOV.

04:08.248 --> 04:09.550
SUSPECTED OF RUNNING
THE LARGEST

04:09.583 --> 04:13.387
PROSTITUTION AND LOAN-SHARKING
OPERATIONS IN THE MIDWEST.

04:13.421 --> 04:16.390
THE BUREAU'S BEEN TRYING TO NAIL
THIS GUY FOR YEARS,

04:16.424 --> 04:18.225
BUT NO ONE WILL TESTIFY.

04:18.258 --> 04:21.429
HE ALSO HAPPENS TO OWN
EASTERN BLOC INTRODUCTIONS.

04:21.462 --> 04:23.564
SO IT'S A FRONT COMYEAH.

04:23.597 --> 04:26.434
WE THINK THAT THE LOAN SHARK'S
ONE OF TUPELOV'S BOYS,

04:26.467 --> 04:28.536
AND LAST NIGHT HE MADE GOOD
ON HIS THREAT.

04:28.569 --> 04:30.504
FRANK COMES HOME,
SEES A BLUE CAMARO

04:30.538 --> 04:32.540
PARKED RIGHT OUTSIDE
HIS HOUSE.

04:32.573 --> 04:34.575
HE GOES INSIDE.
THERE'S AN INTRUDER.

04:34.608 --> 04:36.310
THEY FIGHT.

04:36.344 --> 04:38.412
THE GUY SMASHES FRANK
OVER THE HEAD WITH A LAMP.

04:38.446 --> 04:41.248
THE LIVE-IN MAID
COMES HOME FROM HER NIGHT OFF,

04:41.281 --> 04:42.416
FINDS FRANK UNCONSCIOUS,

04:42.450 --> 04:44.585
CALLS THE COPS,
BUT OLENA IS ALREADY GONE.

04:44.618 --> 04:46.520
[ SCOFFS ] POOR GIRL.

04:46.554 --> 04:48.422
YEAH.

04:49.623 --> 04:51.459
HOW CAN I HELP?

04:51.492 --> 04:53.260
HERE'S THE THING.

04:53.293 --> 04:55.463
FRANK CAN'T GIVE US
A DESCRIPTION OF THIS GUY,

04:55.496 --> 04:57.598
EVEN THOUGH
THEY WERE FACE TO FACE.

04:57.631 --> 05:00.300
WELL, YOU SAID THE INTRUDER
HIT HIM OVER THE HEAD.

05:00.334 --> 05:01.602
THAT COULD CERTAINLY
AFFECT HIS MEMORY.

05:01.635 --> 05:03.471
THAT'S WHY
I BROUGHT THIS TO YOU.

05:03.504 --> 05:04.572
FRANK'S MEMORY IS FINE.

05:04.605 --> 05:06.474
HE CAN DESCRIBE
EVERYTHING

05:06.507 --> 05:08.442
THAT HAPPENED LAST NIGHT
IN PERFECT DETAIL,

05:08.476 --> 05:11.311
SO HOW IS IT THAT HE CAN'T TELL
US WHAT THIS GUY LOOKED LIKE?

05:16.450 --> 05:18.318
[ BEEPING ]

05:24.592 --> 05:26.326
WHAT THE [BLEEP]
IS THAT THING?

05:26.360 --> 05:28.328
WHOLE-BODY-IMAGING
SCANNER.

05:28.362 --> 05:29.663
IT WASN'T HERE
LAST TIME.

05:29.697 --> 05:34.368
YEAH. NEW SECURITY PROTOCOLS.
I'LL MEET YOU ON THE OTHER SIDE.

05:34.402 --> 05:36.437
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

05:36.470 --> 05:38.672
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

05:50.350 --> 05:52.386
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

06:03.564 --> 06:06.567
[ BEEPING INTENSIFIES ]

06:16.376 --> 06:18.612
DANIEL!
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

06:18.646 --> 06:20.648
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA THE
HEALTH RISKS THOSE THINGS POSE?

06:20.681 --> 06:22.683
WH-- THAT?
THAT'S PERFECTLY SAFE.

06:22.716 --> 06:24.685
According to who?
Some government regulatory body?

06:24.718 --> 06:27.387
Like I really trust Uncle Sam
to look out for my well-being.

06:27.421 --> 06:29.490
OKAY, LISTEN, WHAT EXACTLY IS IT
THAT YOU'RE AFRAID OF?

06:29.523 --> 06:32.560
SKIN CANCER, THYROID DISEASE,
MUTATED SPERM.

06:32.593 --> 06:34.361
M-MUTATED SPERM?

06:34.394 --> 06:35.563
NOT TO MENTION
THE VIOLATION OF PRIVACY.

06:35.596 --> 06:37.397
I'M NOT ABOUT TO LET
SOME $10-AN-HOUR RENT-A-COP

06:37.431 --> 06:38.566
CHECK OUT
MY TESTICULAR REGION.

06:39.533 --> 06:41.502
OKAY.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

06:41.535 --> 06:43.571
WE'RE GONNA DO THIS
THE OLD-FASHIONED WAY.

06:47.708 --> 06:49.777
YOU'RE REALLY ENJOYING THIS,
AREN'T YOU?

06:52.480 --> 06:54.448
MR. PRENTICE,
YOU TOLD THE POLICE

06:54.482 --> 06:55.716
THAT YOU STRUGGLED
WITH THE INTRUDER
FOR MORE THAN A MINUTE,

06:55.749 --> 06:58.385
THAT YOU WERE FACE-TO-FACE
THE WHOLE TIME.

06:58.418 --> 07:00.521
ANY DISTINGUISHING FEATURES
OR CHARACTERISTICS?

07:00.554 --> 07:02.690
WELL, I TOLD THEM I'VE NEVER
BEEN TOO GOOD WITH FACES.

07:02.723 --> 07:06.393
THE INTRUDER -- WAS IT THE SAME
MAN YOU'VE BEEN PAYING OFF?

07:06.426 --> 07:08.662
MAYBE. WELL, THEY WERE
ABOUT THE SAME SIZE.

07:08.696 --> 07:10.731
BUT THE GUY
THAT SHAKES ME DOWN

07:10.764 --> 07:12.666
USUALLY WEARS ONE OF THOSE
ORTHODOX CROSSES --

07:12.700 --> 07:14.468
A GOLD ONE ON A CHAIN
AROUND HIS NECK.

07:15.803 --> 07:18.706
WHAT DOES YOUR WIFE
LOOK LIKE?

07:19.707 --> 07:21.475
YOU GOT PICTURES OF HER.

07:21.509 --> 07:22.710
WHAT DOES SHE LOOK LIKE
TO YOU?

07:22.743 --> 07:26.480
BLOND, GOOD-LOOKING.

07:26.514 --> 07:27.748
SHE GOT A GOOD BODY.

07:27.781 --> 07:30.484
D-DO YOU REALLY THINK I'M GONNA
SPEND ALL THAT MONEY

07:30.518 --> 07:32.486
TO BRING HER OVER HERE
IF SHE'S NOT HOT?

07:32.520 --> 07:34.421
THE HUSBAND'S
A REAL CHARMER.

07:34.454 --> 07:36.423
WE FIND THIS GIRL,
AND THEN WHAT?

07:36.456 --> 07:37.758
SHE HAS TO GO BACK
TO THAT?

07:37.791 --> 07:39.426
HERE.
PUT THIS ON.

07:39.459 --> 07:40.628
JUST DO IT.

07:40.661 --> 07:41.629
OKAY.

07:41.662 --> 07:43.597
AND TAKE THESE.

07:43.631 --> 07:45.566
WE'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF AN INTERROGATION.

07:45.599 --> 07:47.434
GO WITH ME ON THIS.

07:47.467 --> 07:51.639
NOW, LET'S DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THAT HAIR.

07:55.643 --> 07:58.712
FRANK, THIS IS MISS JONES.
SHE'S A SKETCH ARTIST.

07:58.746 --> 08:00.514
SHE'S GONNA COME UP
WITH A COMPOSITE

08:00.548 --> 08:02.449
OF THE MAN
WHO ATTACKED YOU.

08:02.482 --> 08:04.484
I SURE AS [BLEEP] HOPE YOU'RE
MORE HELP THAN THAT LAST GIRL.

08:06.687 --> 08:08.789
YOU DON'T RECOGNIZE HER?

08:08.822 --> 08:09.790
WHY?

08:09.823 --> 08:11.759
HAVE WE MET?

08:19.199 --> 08:22.936
IT'S A SENSORY IMPAIRMENT
CALLED PROSOPAGNOSIA,

08:22.970 --> 08:24.905
ALSO KNOWN AS
"FACE BLINDNESS."

08:24.938 --> 08:26.139
EVEN THOUGH FRANK'S VISION
IS PERFECTLY NORMAL,

08:26.173 --> 08:28.008
HE CAN'T RECOGNIZE FACES.

08:28.041 --> 08:29.943
HE PROBABLY COULDN'T PICK
HIS OWN MOTHER OUT OF A LINEUP.

08:29.977 --> 08:31.144
BECAUSE OF THE BLOW
TO THE HEAD?

08:31.178 --> 08:33.814
IT CAN BE CAUSED BY DAMAGE
TO THE FUSIFORM GYRUS,

08:33.847 --> 08:35.849
BUT FRANK SAID HE'D NEVER
BEEN GOOD WITH FACES,

08:35.883 --> 08:37.150
WHICH MEANS
IT'S PROBABLY CONGENITAL.

08:37.184 --> 08:39.052
WAIT A SECOND.

08:39.086 --> 08:40.988
THIS GUY'S HAD THIS BIZARRO
CONDITION HIS ENTIRE LIFE,

08:41.021 --> 08:41.955
AND HE DOESN'T KNOW IT?

08:41.989 --> 08:43.824
HOW'S THAT EVEN POSSIBLE?

08:43.857 --> 08:45.993
MOST PROSOPAGNOSIACS DEVELOP
UNCONSCIOUS STRATEGIES

08:46.026 --> 08:48.028
FOR RECOGNIZING
THE PEOPLE THEY KNOW --

08:48.061 --> 08:51.098
THE WAY THEY DRESS, THE CONTEXT
THEY SEE THEM IN, THEIR VOICE.

08:52.866 --> 08:53.967
GREAT.

08:54.001 --> 08:55.836
WELL, ACCORDING
TO FRANK'S STATEMENT,

08:55.869 --> 08:57.838
THE INTRUDER NEVER SPOKE,
SO EVEN IF WE FIND THE GUY,

08:57.871 --> 08:59.873
OUR WITNESS
CAN'T I.D. HIM.

08:59.907 --> 09:02.943
FRANK SPOKE TO THE LOAN SHARK
AT LEAST HALF A DOZEN TIMES.

09:02.976 --> 09:04.945
HE'D BE ABLE TO RECOGNIZE
HIS VOICE.

09:04.978 --> 09:08.015
WE FIND THE LOAN SHARK, GET
DANIEL TO HELP FRANK I.D. HIM.

09:08.048 --> 09:11.018
WE GRILL HIS SORRY [BLEEP] UNTIL
HE TELLS US WHERE OLENA IS.

09:11.051 --> 09:12.853
CAN I GO NOW?

09:12.886 --> 09:14.221
FRANK COULDN'T PICK ANYBODY
OUT OF THE PHOTO ARRAY.

09:14.254 --> 09:16.990
HOW DO WE KNOW WHICH ONE
OF TUPELOV'S GUYS TO HAUL IN?

09:19.026 --> 09:21.895
HOW ABOUT WE DROP OFF DANIEL
BACK AT CAMPUS

09:21.929 --> 09:23.130
AND GO FIND YOU A WIFE?

09:25.132 --> 09:29.102
WE KNOW THAT YOUR COMPANY
IS A FRONT FOR ALEXEI TUPELOV.

09:29.136 --> 09:32.039
[ Slavic accent ]
HE'S AN INVESTOR. SO?

09:32.072 --> 09:34.875
SO, YOU TWO ARE RUNNING
QUITE A SCAM --

09:34.908 --> 09:36.877
RICH AMERICAN MEN
FOOT THE BILL

09:36.910 --> 09:38.979
FOR PRETTY YOUNG GIRLS
TO EMIGRATE.

09:39.012 --> 09:40.213
THEN YOU
SHAKE THE HUSBANDS DOWN.

09:40.247 --> 09:42.082
AND IF THEY DON'T PAY,

09:42.115 --> 09:44.084
YOU FORCE THEIR IMMIGRANT WIVES
INTO PROSTITUTION.

09:44.117 --> 09:45.085
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

09:45.118 --> 09:46.987
OLENA PRENTICE --

09:47.020 --> 09:49.189
ONE OF TUPELOV'S BOYS THREATENED
TO TAKE HER AS COLLATERAL,

09:49.222 --> 09:51.024
AND NOW SHE'S MISSING.

09:51.058 --> 09:52.225
THAT SOUNDS LIKE CONSPIRACY
TO COMMIT KIDNAPPING

09:52.259 --> 09:54.061
AND EXTORTION TO ME.

09:54.094 --> 09:56.063
DOES THAT SOUND LIKE EXTORTION
TO YOU, ROGER?

09:56.096 --> 09:58.899
IT DOES,
AS A MATTER OF FACT.

09:58.932 --> 10:01.234
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT
KIDNAPPING OR PROSTITUTION.

10:01.268 --> 10:04.037
AND IF YOU ASK ME,
OLENA WENT BACK TO UKRAINE.

10:04.071 --> 10:06.106
YOU THINK
SHE WENT HOME? WHY?

10:06.139 --> 10:08.208
A FEW WEEKS
AFTER SHE GOT HERE,

10:08.241 --> 10:12.012
SHE CALLED ME TO SAY
THAT FRANK WAS VERY MEAN TO HER.

10:12.045 --> 10:14.081
HE DID NOT
LET HER LEAVE THE HOUSE.

10:14.114 --> 10:16.083
SO SHE WANTED OUT.

10:16.116 --> 10:17.918
SO YOU HELPED HER,
OF COURSE.

10:17.951 --> 10:19.086
[ SIGHS ]

10:19.119 --> 10:23.090
I'M A MARRIAGE BROKER,
NOT A MARRIAGE COUNSELOR.

10:23.123 --> 10:26.226
I TOLD HER TO STICK IT OUT,
TO STAY A FEW YEARS,

10:26.259 --> 10:28.061
THEN DIVORCE HIM,
TAKE HIS MONEY.

10:28.095 --> 10:29.930
IT'S THE AMERICAN WAY,
RIGHT?

10:29.963 --> 10:33.934
THERE IS AN INNOCENT YOUNG GIRL
MISSING WHO CAME TO THIS COUNTRY

10:33.967 --> 10:35.268
TRYING TO MAKE A BETTER LIFE
FOR HERSELF.

10:35.302 --> 10:37.237
YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE
FOR BRINGING HER HERE,

10:37.270 --> 10:39.973
AND YOU COULDN'T BE BOTHERED
TO HELP HER WHEN SHE ASKED.

10:41.141 --> 10:43.110
WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM ME?

10:43.143 --> 10:46.046
I WANT THE NAME OF THE MAN
WHO WAS SHAKING FRANK DOWN.

10:46.079 --> 10:48.115
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THAT I --

10:48.148 --> 10:51.151
IF YOU DON'T GIVE ME A NAME,
THIS PLACE IS GONNA BE SWARMING

10:51.184 --> 10:54.087
WITH I.C.E. AGENTS,
U.S. ATTORNEYS, I.R.S.

10:54.121 --> 10:56.189
YOU WILL GO TO FEDERAL PRISON,
KICKING YOURSELF

10:56.223 --> 10:59.059
FOR NOT COOPERATING
WITH THAT NICE GIRL FROM THE FBI

10:59.092 --> 11:00.160
WHEN YOU HAD THE CHANCE.

11:02.329 --> 11:06.099
Kate:
YURI PETROVICH?

11:06.133 --> 11:07.300
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI,
FBI.

11:07.334 --> 11:08.969
OH, FBI, HUH?

11:09.002 --> 11:11.171
I MUST BE
MOVING UP IN THE WORLD.

11:11.204 --> 11:13.273
WE'RE LOOKING FOR A MISSING
WOMAN -- OLENA PRENTICE.

11:13.306 --> 11:15.175
I GOT ALL THE WOMEN I NEED
RIGHT HERE.

11:15.208 --> 11:17.210
NEVER HEARD OF NO OLENA.

11:17.244 --> 11:19.980
YEAH, THAT'S FUNNY,
BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN SHAKING DOWN

11:20.013 --> 11:22.149
HER HUSBAND, FRANK, THREATENING
TO TURN OUT HIS WIFE.

11:22.182 --> 11:24.117
Roger: OKAY, THANKS.

11:24.151 --> 11:26.353
A BODY MATCHING THE DESCRIPTION
OF OLENA PRENTICE

11:26.386 --> 11:29.089
WAS JUST FOUND IN A LANDFILL
OUT BY MIDWAY.

11:29.122 --> 11:31.091
CONGRATULATIONS, YURI.

11:31.124 --> 11:33.260
YOU JUST BECAME
THE PRIME SUSPECT IN
A MURDER INVESTIGATION.

11:37.164 --> 11:38.999
PAUL, YOU WANTED TO SEE --

11:39.032 --> 11:40.200
DANIEL! PERFECT TIMING.
COME IN.

11:40.233 --> 11:42.035
SAY HELLO
TO DR. MICHAEL HATHAWAY.

11:42.069 --> 11:43.236
I'VE BEEN
TRYING TO CONVINCE MICHAEL

11:43.270 --> 11:45.038
TO BRING HIS TALENTS
TO THE SOUTH SIDE

11:45.072 --> 11:47.107
AND BECOME THE NEWEST MEMBER
OF OUR ESTEEMED FACULTY.

11:47.140 --> 11:48.141
IT'S AN HONOR.

11:50.377 --> 11:52.179
RIGHT.

11:52.212 --> 11:56.016
YOU'RE THE, UH, FAMOUS
SELF-HELP SAGE TO THE STARS.

11:56.049 --> 11:59.052
WELL, MY ACADEMIC SPECIALTY'S
BEHAVIORAL SCIENCE, OF COURSE.

11:59.086 --> 12:01.121
THE "SAGE" PART
WAS MY PUBLICISTS' IDEA.

12:01.154 --> 12:02.222
I FOUGHT THEM ON IT,

12:02.255 --> 12:04.157
BUT IT MOVED SOME BOOKS,
SO WHAT DO I KNOW?

12:04.191 --> 12:07.027
YOU KNOW, MICHAEL'S HAD
A NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER

12:07.060 --> 12:08.028
THREE YEARS RUNNING.

12:08.061 --> 12:09.362
IS THAT RIGHT?

12:09.396 --> 12:11.198
I'VE READ ALL YOUR BOOKS.

12:11.231 --> 12:12.365
YEAH, IN FACT,
WHEN PAUL RANG WITH HIS OFFER,

12:12.399 --> 12:14.134
I SAID
I'D ONLY CONSIDER IT

12:14.167 --> 12:16.036
IF IT MEANT A CHANCE
TO WORK WITH YOU.

12:16.069 --> 12:18.405
UH, I READ
YOUR LAST BOOK, TOO.

12:23.243 --> 12:24.344
IT WAS BRILLIANT...

12:24.377 --> 12:26.079
W-WASN'T IT, DANIEL?

12:26.113 --> 12:27.280
NO. NO.

12:27.314 --> 12:30.250
I-I THOUGHT IT WAS A MUDDLED
MESS OF SHODDY RESEARCH,

12:30.283 --> 12:32.219
JUNK SCIENCE,
AND PEDANTIC PLATITUDES,

12:32.252 --> 12:34.254
BUT I HOPE YOU ENJOY
YOUR TIME IN CHICAGO.

12:34.287 --> 12:37.290
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, I HAVE SOME
ACTUAL SCHOLARSHIP TO ATTEND TO.

12:39.192 --> 12:40.227
RIGHT.

12:40.260 --> 12:42.362
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

12:44.431 --> 12:46.233
DOC.

12:46.266 --> 12:48.168
OH, I WENT
TO THE [BLEEP] MEETING.

12:48.201 --> 12:50.170
WHAT THE [BLEEP] ELSE
DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

12:50.203 --> 12:51.371
AGENT MORETTI CALLED,

12:51.404 --> 12:53.306
SAYS THEY WANT YOU
TO HELP I.D. A SUSPECT.

12:53.340 --> 12:55.075
[ SIGHS ]

12:55.108 --> 12:57.410
ALL RIGHT. GET THE CAR.
I'LL GET MY COAT.

13:03.283 --> 13:06.219
Man: [ Slavic accent ]
HELLO, DR. PIERCE.

13:07.454 --> 13:09.089
MAY I HELP YOU?

13:09.122 --> 13:12.225
MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU,
PROFESSOR.

13:13.293 --> 13:16.263
FRIENDLY ADVICE --
WON'T COST YOU NOTHING.

13:16.296 --> 13:20.400
IT'S BETTER FOR EVERYONE --
YOU, ESPECIALLY --

13:20.433 --> 13:24.204
IF YOU DON'T HELP FBI
ON THIS CASE NO MORE.

13:24.237 --> 13:26.106
[ SCOFFS ]

13:26.139 --> 13:27.307
HOW DO YOU KNOW I'M...

13:27.340 --> 13:31.378
WE HAVE MANY FRIENDS,
EVEN AT FBI.

13:33.280 --> 13:34.414
YOU HAVE A MOLE.

13:34.447 --> 13:36.283
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:36.316 --> 13:37.350
A MOLE.

13:37.384 --> 13:40.120
WE'RE NOT KGB,
BUT, YES...

13:40.153 --> 13:42.389
I SUPPOSE
YOU COULD SAY THIS.

13:44.491 --> 13:49.262
I HEAR YOU ARE
A VERY SMART MAN, PROFESSOR.

13:49.296 --> 13:54.167
SO I THINK YOU KNOW
IT IS NOT HEALTHY

13:54.201 --> 13:55.502
FOR YOU TO WORK
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

13:58.171 --> 14:03.410
AFTER ALL, YOU DON'T WANT
TO ALSO DISAPPEAR, DO YOU?

14:06.479 --> 14:08.515
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

14:15.022 --> 14:17.157
DO ANY OF THESE MEN
REMIND YOU OF THE MAN

14:17.190 --> 14:19.159
WHO THREATENED
TO HURT YOUR WIFE?

14:19.192 --> 14:23.230
ANYTHING STAND OUT?
HANDS, HAIRLINE, POSTURE?

14:28.235 --> 14:30.037
NUMBER 2.

14:30.070 --> 14:31.138
WHY HIM?

14:31.171 --> 14:33.173
I RECOGNIZE
THAT WIDOW'S PEAK,

14:33.206 --> 14:35.208
THOSE SCRAWNY,
BOWED LEGS.

14:35.242 --> 14:38.111
I WANT THAT [BLEEP] TO PAY
FOR WHAT HE DID TO MY WIFE.

14:38.145 --> 14:40.880
Kate: THAT'S GOOD. IT'S THE SAME
GUY WHOSE VOICE YOU I.D.'d.

14:40.914 --> 14:43.216
DANIEL, CAN YOU TESTIFY IN COURT
THAT THE VISUAL I.D. IS VALID

14:43.250 --> 14:47.020
DESPITE MR. PRENTICE'S
CONDITION?

14:47.054 --> 14:49.222
DANIEL. YES OR NO?
IS THE I.D. SOLID?

14:49.256 --> 14:51.959
YES, I -- I'LL STAND BY IT.

14:54.962 --> 14:57.064
I'M GONNA LAY IT OUT
FOR YOU, YURI.

14:57.097 --> 15:02.302
YOU GOT PRIORS --
PIMPING, EXTORTION, ASSAULT.

15:02.335 --> 15:04.137
FRANK PRENTICE
JUST FINGERED YOU

15:04.171 --> 15:06.206
AS THE MAN WHO THREATENED
TO ABDUCT HIS WIFE.

15:06.239 --> 15:08.041
SHE DISAPPEARED.
NOW SHE'S DEAD.

15:08.075 --> 15:12.912
WHAT DO YOU MAKE?
$40,000, $45,000 A YEAR?

15:12.946 --> 15:15.215
YOU'RE A HOT
LITTLE SPINNER.

15:15.248 --> 15:18.151
COME WORK FOR ME.
YOU COULD EARN SOME REAL MONEY.

15:18.185 --> 15:21.154
AN INNOCENT GIRL
WAS KILLED, YURI.

15:21.188 --> 15:24.024
NOW, IN ADDITION TO THE FACT
THAT IT REALLY [BLEEP] ME OFF,

15:24.057 --> 15:26.193
IT'S ALSO MURDER DURING
THE COMMISSION OF A FELONY.

15:26.226 --> 15:28.962
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS?

15:28.996 --> 15:30.197
DEATH PENALTY.

15:30.230 --> 15:33.100
AND I FOR ONE AM NOT GONNA
BE CRYING AT YOUR FUNERAL.

15:36.136 --> 15:38.938
BUT MAYBE...

15:38.972 --> 15:41.941
YOU DIDN'T
MEAN TO KILL HER.

15:41.975 --> 15:43.243
YEAH, THE MEDICAL
EXAMINER SAYS

15:43.276 --> 15:46.246
THAT SHE DIED FROM A BLOW
TO THE BASE OF THE SKULL.

15:46.279 --> 15:48.281
MAYBE SHE WAS
TRYING TO GET AWAY.

15:48.315 --> 15:51.118
MAYBE SHE FELL,
HIT HER HEAD.

15:51.151 --> 15:53.120
NOW YOU'RE ONLY LOOKING
AT INVOLUNTARY MANSLAUGHTER.

15:53.153 --> 15:55.122
YOU MIGHT ONLY DO
18 MONTHS.

15:55.155 --> 15:58.125
YOU'RE OFFERING ME A DEAL,
JUST 'CAUSE YOU'RE SWEET ON ME?

15:58.158 --> 16:00.060
YOU'RE TOO SMALL
FOR ME, YURI --

16:00.093 --> 16:02.029
IN MORE WAYS THAN ONE,
I WOULD BET.

16:03.030 --> 16:04.197
[ SCOFFS ]

16:04.231 --> 16:06.966
NO, I WANT
SOMETHING BIGGER.

16:07.000 --> 16:08.301
I WANT ALEXEI TUPELOV.

16:08.335 --> 16:10.303
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]

16:10.337 --> 16:12.239
[BLEEP]
WHAT ARE YOU SMOKING?

16:12.272 --> 16:15.142
I RAT OUT TUPELOV, I MIGHT
AS WELL GET THE DEATH PENALTY.

16:15.175 --> 16:16.309
OKAY.

16:16.343 --> 16:19.079
WE'VE ALREADY GOT YOU
ON THE EXTORTION.

16:19.112 --> 16:22.082
IT'S UP TO FIVE YEARS
FOR EACH COUNT.

16:22.115 --> 16:24.351
I HOPE YOU ENJOY
YOUR STAY AT MARION.

16:27.120 --> 16:29.222
Roger: DO YOU THINK
HE'S GONNA GIVE US TUPELOV?

16:29.256 --> 16:32.159
IT WOULD HELP IF WE COULD
CONNECT HIM TO THE CRIME SCENE.

16:32.192 --> 16:33.993
ANY LUCK
ON THE BLUE CAMARO?

16:34.027 --> 16:35.995
YURI DRIVES AN [ SIGHS ]

16:36.029 --> 16:38.298
I DOUBT YURI AND HIS BOYS
WOULD BE STUPID ENOUGH

16:38.331 --> 16:42.335
TO COMMIT KIDNAPPING
IN A REGISTERED CAR.

16:42.369 --> 16:45.138
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

16:52.279 --> 16:54.147
EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT,
DR. PIERCE?

16:54.181 --> 16:56.049
YES, I'M FINE.

16:59.152 --> 17:00.353
THAT PENDANT.

17:00.387 --> 17:03.256
YURI PETROVICH
HAS ONE JUST LIKE IT.

17:03.290 --> 17:06.326
WELL, I GREW UP WITH A LOT
OF THE GUYS IN TUPELOV'S CREW.

17:06.359 --> 17:09.162
THAT'S WHY I WAS PICKED
FOR THE TASK FORCE.

17:10.397 --> 17:13.333
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

17:13.366 --> 17:17.070
DID YURI
REALLY KILL OLENA?

17:18.171 --> 17:20.173
WHO ELSE
COULD HAVE DONE IT?

17:20.207 --> 17:23.076
WELL, LET'S JUST SAY
SOME FRIENDS OF MINE
WOULD BE VERY GRATEFUL

17:23.110 --> 17:25.345
IF YOU DIDN'T HELP MORETTI
PIN THIS MURDER ON YURI.

17:26.479 --> 17:28.215
YOU'RE THE MOLE.

17:28.248 --> 17:31.050
NO. NOT ME, PROFESSOR.

17:31.084 --> 17:33.386
BUT YOU'RE RIGHT.
THERE IS A MOLE.

17:33.420 --> 17:35.355
WHO?

17:37.390 --> 17:39.092
DANIEL.

17:41.094 --> 17:43.062
GIVE YOU A LIFT BACK?

17:43.096 --> 17:44.063
YEAH.

17:44.097 --> 17:45.365
SURE..

17:48.135 --> 17:51.070
Natalie: YOU'RE BEING THREATENED
BY A RUSSIAN MOBSTER,

17:51.104 --> 17:53.206
AND YOU DON'T BOTHER
MENTIONING IT TO KATE?

17:53.240 --> 17:54.407
WHY NOT?

17:54.441 --> 17:57.310
'CAUSE HE'S PROBABLY
A [BLEEP] HALLUCINATION --

17:57.344 --> 18:00.380
THE SAME AS THE LADY AGENT
TURNED OUT TO BE.

18:00.413 --> 18:04.184
I JUST -- I DON'T WANT KATE
TO THINK I'M BONKERS.

18:04.217 --> 18:05.485
WELL, IF YOU'RE SO CONVINCED
THAT HE WASN'T REAL,

18:05.518 --> 18:07.254
why do you keep looking
out the window?!

18:07.287 --> 18:09.222
Because I might be wrong!

18:09.256 --> 18:11.124
W-what if there really is
a goon out there

18:11.158 --> 18:12.392
waiting to break
my kneecaps?

18:12.425 --> 18:16.196
DANIEL, YOU AND I BOTH KNOW
THAT FEELING THREATENED

18:16.229 --> 18:19.098
BY A CRIMINAL CONSPIRACY
STRAIGHT OUT OF A SPY NOVEL

18:19.132 --> 18:21.401
IS CLASSIC
SCHIZOPHRENIC DELUSION.

18:21.434 --> 18:25.405
WHAT'S MORE PLAUSIBLE --
THAT THERE'S A FIENDISH PLOT

18:25.438 --> 18:28.375
WITH MOBSTERS
AND CORRUPT FBI AGENTS

18:28.408 --> 18:30.277
OR THAT YOU'RE
IMAGINING IT?

18:36.449 --> 18:38.285
THANK YOU
FOR BEING HERE.

18:38.318 --> 18:40.253
THAT'S WHAT FRIENDS
ARE FOR.

18:40.287 --> 18:43.456
YOU SAID THIS THUG TOLD YOU
THAT IT WASN'T HEALTHY

18:43.490 --> 18:46.393
FOR YOU TO KEEP WORKING
FOR THE FBI.

18:46.426 --> 18:49.128
IT SOUNDS LIKE A MANIFESTATION
OF YOUR ANXIETY

18:49.162 --> 18:51.164
ABOUT GETTING INVOLVED
WITH THESE CASES,

18:51.198 --> 18:53.300
BECAUSE YOU KNOW
THEY GET YOU OFF YOUR ROUTINE

18:53.333 --> 18:55.134
AND TRIGGER EPISODES.

18:55.168 --> 18:58.171
HE ALSO SAID I MIGHT DISAPPEAR.
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT?

18:58.205 --> 19:00.373
LAST TIME YOU
CHECKED INTO REXFORD,

19:00.407 --> 19:02.275
YOU DIDN'T TELL ANYBODY
WHERE YOU WERE --

19:02.309 --> 19:04.143
YOUR FRIENDS,
YOUR STUDENTS.

19:04.177 --> 19:07.180
YOU JUST DISAPPEARED
OUT OF THEIR LIVES.

19:07.214 --> 19:10.149
SO, I'M NOT AFRAID
OF UKRAINIAN GANGSTERS

19:10.183 --> 19:13.186
SO MUCH AS ORDERLIES
WITH BUTTERFLY NETS?

19:14.321 --> 19:17.156
YOU'RE NOT GOING BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL.

19:17.190 --> 19:18.458
YOU HAVE ME,
YOU HAVE LEWICKI,

19:18.491 --> 19:20.493
AND YOU'RE MANAGING
YOUR CONDITION.

19:20.527 --> 19:22.262
[ SIGHS ]

19:22.295 --> 19:25.265
SOME DAYS I MANAGE
BETTER THAN OTHERS.

19:25.298 --> 19:27.434
YOUR SYMPTOMS ARE MORE ACUTE
WHEN YOUR SUBCONSCIOUS

19:27.467 --> 19:30.237
IS WORKING ON A PROBLEM
THAT IT CAN'T QUITE SOLVE.

19:31.538 --> 19:35.208
THE UKRAINIAN GUY
SAID THERE WAS A MOLE.

19:35.242 --> 19:37.510
NOW, IT'S NOT THE AGENT,
OBVIOUSLY.

19:37.544 --> 19:40.179
WELL, MAYBE IT'S A RIDDLE.
WHAT'S A MOLE?

19:40.213 --> 19:44.451
A SPY, AN IMPOSTER, SOMEONE
WHO HIDES IN PLAIN SIGHT.

19:44.484 --> 19:47.287
BUT THERE'S
ANOTHER KIND OF MOLE --

19:47.320 --> 19:50.223
THE KIND THAT BURROWS
UNDERGROUND.

19:51.391 --> 19:52.459
MOLES ARE BLIND.

19:52.492 --> 19:54.193
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

19:54.227 --> 19:56.229
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT TIME IT IS?

19:56.263 --> 19:58.365
YURI DIDN'T KILL
OLENA PRENTICE.

19:58.398 --> 20:00.300
WHAT?

20:00.333 --> 20:03.436
YOU WOKE ME UP AT...

20:03.470 --> 20:06.306
3:18 A.M.

20:06.339 --> 20:08.375
TO ACCUSE ME
OF TRYING TO COERCE A CONFESSION

20:08.408 --> 20:09.509
OUT OF AN INNOCENT MAN?

20:09.542 --> 20:11.378
THAT SCUMBAG
IS ANYTHING BUT INNOCENT,

20:11.411 --> 20:13.346
BUT THAT DOES NOT MAKE HIM
THE KILLER.

20:14.514 --> 20:15.548
OKAY, DANIEL.

20:15.582 --> 20:17.617
IF THE LYING, PIMPING,
SADISTIC FELON

20:17.650 --> 20:21.454
WHO THREATENED TO ABDUCT OLENA
DIDN'T KILL HER, THEN WHO DID?

20:21.488 --> 20:22.522
HER HUSBAND.

20:22.555 --> 20:24.524
HE PASSED A POLYGRAPH.

20:24.557 --> 20:25.525
HE'S FACE-BLIND!

20:25.558 --> 20:27.394
FOR ALL WE KNOW, HE --

20:27.427 --> 20:29.529
HE KILLED HIS OWN WIFE
WITHOUT REALIZING IT WAS HER.

20:29.562 --> 20:33.333
BUT YOU JUST PROVED THAT
PROSOPAGNOSIACS CAN I.D. PEOPLE

20:33.366 --> 20:36.235
BY THEIR VOICE OR THEIR POSTURE
OR WHATEVER.

20:36.269 --> 20:38.371
HE WOULD HAVE KNOWN
HIS OWN WIFE.

20:38.405 --> 20:41.240
MAYBE SHE WAS WEARING
SOME KIND OF DISGUISE.

20:41.274 --> 20:44.277
[ Laughing ] WHAT IS THIS?
IS THIS, LIKE, A SPY NOVEL?

20:44.311 --> 20:46.579
DON'T -- I'M JUST...

20:46.613 --> 20:48.548
I'M JUST SAYING --
I'M JUST SAYING IT'S POSSIBLE.

20:48.581 --> 20:50.350
OKAY, DANIEL.

20:50.383 --> 20:52.251
WHY WOULD OLENA
HAVE BEEN WEARING A DISGUISE?

20:52.285 --> 20:54.421
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE SHE
WAS TRYING TO GET AWAY FROM HIM.

20:54.454 --> 20:55.588
YOU SAID YOURSELF
HOW AWFUL HE IS.

20:55.622 --> 20:59.292
THE MARRIAGE BROKER DID SAY
THAT SHE WANTED OUT.

20:59.326 --> 21:02.429
YOU SEE? YOU SEE?
SO SHE RUNS AWAY.

21:02.462 --> 21:06.366
FRANK REALIZES THAT -- THAT
HIS PRIZED POSSESSION IS GONE,

21:06.399 --> 21:08.535
AFTER ALL THE DEBT HE'S RUN UP
AND THREATS HE'S ENDURED

21:08.568 --> 21:10.437
FROM YURI --
ALL OF IT FOR HER.

21:10.470 --> 21:12.439
SO HE TRACKS THE UNGRATEFUL
[BLEEP] DOWN, AND HE KILLS HER.

21:12.472 --> 21:14.607
EXCEPT THERE'S A FLAW
IN YOUR THEORY.

21:14.641 --> 21:17.544
IF FRANK KILLED HIS WIFE FOR THE
REASONS THAT YOU JUST LAID OUT,

21:17.577 --> 21:20.279
HE WOULD HAVE KNOWN THAT IT WAS
HER WHO HE WAS KILLING,

21:20.313 --> 21:22.281
AND HE WOULDN'T HAVE PASSED
A POLY, FACE-BLIND OR NOT.

21:22.315 --> 21:23.450
RIGHT.

21:23.483 --> 21:25.618
SO, UH, FRANK THOUGHT
SHE WAS KIDNAPPED,

21:25.652 --> 21:28.455
SO MAYBE HE DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT SHE'D RUN AWAY

21:28.488 --> 21:30.523
UNTIL AFTER
HE TOOK THE POLYGRAPH.

21:30.557 --> 21:32.592
THEN -- THEN
HE FIGURES OUT THE TRUTH,

21:32.625 --> 21:35.294
AND HE TRACKS HER DOWN,
AND HE KILLS HER.

21:35.328 --> 21:36.529
NICE.

21:36.563 --> 21:39.466
EXCEPT THE MEDICAL EXAMINER
PUTS HER TIME OF DEATH

21:39.499 --> 21:40.600
BEFORE HE TOOK THE EXAM.

21:40.633 --> 21:42.535
OKAY.
SO -- SO -- THE -- THE --

21:42.569 --> 21:45.572
OKAY. FORGET IT.
FORGET IT. FORGET IT.

21:45.605 --> 21:47.574
NO, I JUST -- YOU KNOW --
GO -- GO BACK TO THAT.

21:47.607 --> 21:50.410
I'M SURE YOU'LL SLEEP THE SLEEP
OF THE JUST KNOWING THAT --

21:50.443 --> 21:51.611
THAT THE PUZZLE'S
BEEN SOLVED

21:51.644 --> 21:54.313
AND THAT YOU'VE NAILED
THE RIGHT GUY FOR THE MURDER.

21:54.347 --> 21:55.648
WELL, I AM AWAKE ALREADY.

21:55.682 --> 21:57.517
WELL, THEN, LET'S GO.

21:58.585 --> 22:00.520
I'M GONNA
PUT SOME PANTS ON FIRST.

22:04.357 --> 22:05.525
YOUR APARTMENT'S NICE.

22:09.796 --> 22:11.498
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

22:13.400 --> 22:15.368
[ Slavic accent ]
MAY I HELP YOU?

22:15.402 --> 22:17.770
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI, FBI.
THIS IS DR. PIERCE.

22:17.804 --> 22:21.608
AND YOU ARE, UH, MASHA, THE
PRENTICES' HOUSEKEEPER, CORRECT?

22:21.641 --> 22:22.609
YES.

22:22.642 --> 22:23.710
COME IN.

22:25.712 --> 22:30.750
SO, YOU'RE THE ONE WHO FOUND
MR. PRENTICE UNCONSCIOUS?

22:30.783 --> 22:31.751
YES.

22:31.784 --> 22:34.654
COME HOME FROM MOVIES.

22:34.687 --> 22:37.724
SEE HIM ON FLOOR
WITH BLOOD.

22:39.626 --> 22:40.760
FIRST I THINK
HE IS DEAD.

22:40.793 --> 22:42.495
AND OLENA?

22:42.529 --> 22:43.630
I CALL AMBULANCE.

22:43.663 --> 22:45.765
THEN I LOOK FOR HER.
SHE'S NOT HERE.

22:45.798 --> 22:47.667
I SEE
YOU'RE PACKING.

22:47.700 --> 22:50.703
I SEND OLENA'S CLOTHES
TO HER SISTERS IN UKRAINE,

22:50.737 --> 22:52.472
THEN I FIND OTHER JOB.

22:52.505 --> 22:54.707
YOU WON'T BE STAYING ON
WITH MR. PRENTICE?

22:54.741 --> 23:00.613
OLENA SPEAK LITTLE ENGLISH.
THEY HIRE ME SO I TRANSLATE.

23:00.647 --> 23:02.549
NOW SHE'S GONE.

23:02.582 --> 23:05.485
OLENA DIDN'T HAVE ANY FAMILY
HERE IN THE STATES?

23:05.518 --> 23:08.555
SHE HAVE COUSIN --
PAULINA.

23:08.588 --> 23:11.791
SHE COME HERE TO VISIT
BEFORE I WORK HERE,

23:11.824 --> 23:15.795
BUT MR. PRENTICE NOT LIKE HER,
TELL HER TO GO AWAY.

23:15.828 --> 23:19.632
DOESN'T SOUND LIKE OLENA WAS
VERY HAPPY WITH MR. PRENTICE.

23:19.666 --> 23:22.435
MR. PRENTICE
NOT LET HER GO ANYWHERE.

23:22.469 --> 23:26.439
HE SAY IT IS NOT SAFE, BUT
HE WORK ALWAYS UNTIL VERY LATE.

23:26.473 --> 23:29.576
UNTIL I COME,
OLENA WAS ALONE.

23:32.479 --> 23:33.746
DID HE EVER HURT HER?

23:35.482 --> 23:36.749
SOMETIMES HE HIT HER.

23:42.489 --> 23:45.658
DO YOU THINK IT'S POSSIBLE
SHE WASN'T KIDNAPPED --

23:45.692 --> 23:47.460
THAT MAYBE SHE RAN AWAY?

23:47.494 --> 23:48.728
BUT...

23:48.761 --> 23:52.465
THERE WAS UKRAINIAN MAN ARRESTED
FOR HER MURDER, NO?

23:52.499 --> 23:53.733
DANIEL.

23:57.704 --> 23:59.839
"THANKS FOR
TAKING CARE OF THIS, BABY.

23:59.872 --> 24:02.609
HUGS AND KISSES.
JOLENE."

24:02.642 --> 24:03.876
WHO'S JOLENE?

24:05.745 --> 24:07.680
I NEVER HEAR THIS NAME.

24:07.714 --> 24:10.883
WELL, WHOEVER SHE IS, FRANK'S
PAYING HER CREDIT-CARD BILLS.

24:17.590 --> 24:18.491
[ DOOR OPENS ]

24:18.525 --> 24:19.792
JOLENE GREY?

24:19.826 --> 24:22.695
I'M SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI.
THIS IS DR. DANIEL PIERCE.

24:22.729 --> 24:24.731
THANK YOU FOR AGREEING
TO COME TALK TO US.

24:24.764 --> 24:27.500
I'LL TELL YOU WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO KNOW,

24:27.534 --> 24:29.569
BUT, PLEASE,
DON'T TELL MY HUSBAND.

24:29.602 --> 24:30.603
OKAY.

24:30.637 --> 24:32.705
YOU COOPERATE WITH US,

24:32.739 --> 24:35.608
AND, UH, WE'LL DO WHAT WE CAN
TO KEEP THINGS DISCREET.

24:35.642 --> 24:36.809
THANK YOU.

24:37.910 --> 24:42.715
NOW, THIS IS SOME TAB
YOU'VE RUN UP HERE.

24:42.749 --> 24:47.620
FANCY HOTELS, JEWELRY,
CASH ADVANCES.

24:48.788 --> 24:51.524
I LOST MY WALLET
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

24:51.558 --> 24:54.527
SOMEONE MUST HAVE STOLEN MY I.D.
AND OPENED THIS ACCOUNT.

24:54.561 --> 24:55.662
YEAH, SEE,
THAT'S NOT REALLY

24:55.695 --> 24:56.929
THE WAY IDENTITY THEFT
WORKS, JOLENE.

24:56.963 --> 24:58.898
CRIMINALS RUN UP TABS
UNDER SOMEONE ELSE'S NAME,

24:58.931 --> 25:01.634
AND THEN
THEY DON'T PAY THE BILL.

25:01.668 --> 25:04.604
I'M TELLING YOU,
THESE AREN'T MY CHARGES.

25:04.637 --> 25:07.540
MY HUSBAND TOOK AWAY
MY CREDIT CARDS LAST YEAR.

25:07.574 --> 25:09.842
SO YOU GOT ANOTHER ONE --
PAID FOR EVERY MONTH

25:09.876 --> 25:12.745
WITH CHECKS FROM
FRANK PRENTICE'S
BUSINESS ACCOUNT.

25:12.779 --> 25:14.747
I DON'T KNOW
ANY FRANK PRENTICE.

25:14.781 --> 25:16.549
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
GONNA COOPERATE, JOLENE.

25:16.583 --> 25:18.651
NOW, ACCORDING TO
YOUR CELLPHONE RECORDS,

25:18.685 --> 25:20.687
YOU'VE CALLED FRANK
SEVERAL TIMES A DAY

25:20.720 --> 25:21.854
FOR THE PAST FEW MONTHS.

25:21.888 --> 25:24.557
I'M ON A FAMILY PLAN.
MY HUSBAND PAYS THE BILL.

25:24.591 --> 25:27.627
SO YOU GOT A SECOND PHONE,
RESERVED FOR A SPECIAL CALLER.

25:27.660 --> 25:29.662
AFTER ALL, YOU WOULDN'T WANT
FRANK'S NUMBER

25:29.696 --> 25:30.930
SHOWING UP
ON YOUR HUSBAND'S BILL.

25:30.963 --> 25:34.834
OR MAYBE YOU WERE JEALOUS
OF FRANK'S WIFE.

25:34.867 --> 25:36.803
MAYBE USED
ONE OF THOSE CASH ADVANCES

25:36.836 --> 25:39.572
TO PAY SOMEONE TO MAKE
OLENA PRENTICE DISAPPEAR.

25:39.606 --> 25:41.841
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

25:41.874 --> 25:44.844
CHECK OUT THOSE HEELS.

25:46.813 --> 25:48.881
MUST HAVE COST HER
A FORTUNE.

25:48.915 --> 25:51.784
TELL ME THE TRUTH,
JOLENE.

25:51.818 --> 25:53.586
WHERE DID YOU GET
THOSE SHOES?

25:53.620 --> 25:54.787
DANIEL?

25:54.821 --> 25:55.822
THEY'RE BEAUTIFUL.

25:57.023 --> 25:59.792
THANK YOU.
MARSHALL FIELD'S.

25:59.826 --> 26:01.594
DID YOU PAY CASH
FOR THEM?

26:01.628 --> 26:03.796
YES.
HOW DID YOU --

26:03.830 --> 26:05.865
WELL, YOUR HUSBAND
TOOK YOUR CREDIT CARDS.

26:05.898 --> 26:09.902
JOLENE, DO YOU SOMETIMES
BUY THINGS

26:09.936 --> 26:13.773
TO MAKE YOURSELF FEEL BETTER --
CLOTHING OR JEWELRY?

26:16.008 --> 26:18.010
[ Crying ]
I AM SO SORRY.

26:19.779 --> 26:22.615
AND DID YOU NEED THOSE SHOES
SO BADLY

26:22.649 --> 26:24.851
THAT YOU STOLE MONEY
TO BUY THEM?

26:24.884 --> 26:26.986
YES.

26:27.019 --> 26:29.722
I THOUGHT THAT'S
WHAT THIS WAS ABOUT.

26:29.756 --> 26:31.624
I'LL PAY BACK EVERY PENNY.

26:31.658 --> 26:33.793
PLEASE.
DON'T TELL MY HUSBAND.

26:36.663 --> 26:39.666
COMPULSIVE BUYING
DISORDER.

26:42.735 --> 26:45.705
Roger: ONE OF OUR AGENTS SHOWED
JOLENE'S PHOTO TO THE DESK CLERK

26:45.738 --> 26:47.006
AT THE HOTEL
WHERE THE GOLD CARD WAS USED.

26:47.039 --> 26:48.775
SAID HE'S NEVER
SEEN HER BEFORE.

26:48.808 --> 26:51.644
BUT A DIFFERENT WOMAN
CHECKED IN REGULARLY

26:51.678 --> 26:53.012
USING JOLENE'S NAME,
MET FRANK THERE.

26:53.045 --> 26:55.882
BOTH WOMEN HAVE BLACK HAIR,
BUT ACCORDING TO THE DESK CLERK,

26:55.915 --> 26:57.750
THE OTHER ONE IS
"WAY HOTTER."

26:57.784 --> 27:01.854
I WAS RIGHT THE FIRST TIME.
"MOLE" MEANS "IMPOSTER."

27:01.888 --> 27:03.923
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

27:03.956 --> 27:07.860
MAYBE THIS IMPOSTER GOT HERSELF
A WIG OR A DYE JOB,

27:07.894 --> 27:09.862
DID SOMETHING
TO MAKE HERSELF LOOK

27:09.896 --> 27:12.031
ENOUGH LIKE JOLENE'S
DRIVER'S-LICENSE PHOTO

27:12.064 --> 27:13.966
TO FOOL ANYONE WHO DIDN'T
LOOK TOO CLOSELY.

27:25.812 --> 27:28.748
SHE MADE CHARGES EVERY
TUESDAY AND THURSDAY LAST MONTH

27:28.781 --> 27:30.950
AT A PLACE
CALLED THE RED RABBLE.

27:30.983 --> 27:33.786
THAT'S A BAR OFF I-90.

27:33.820 --> 27:35.688
AND TODAY'S THURSDAY.

27:35.722 --> 27:37.824
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS IN DISTANCE ]

27:44.731 --> 27:48.067
THAT'S RIGHT, PROFESSOR.
I'M FOLLOWING YOU.

27:48.100 --> 27:50.937
HOW DO YOU LIKE
MY NEW AMERICAN CAR?

27:52.038 --> 27:53.906
Kate: DANIEL?

27:53.940 --> 27:55.041
WHAT'S GOING ON?

27:56.108 --> 27:57.810
LOOK.

27:57.844 --> 27:59.078
A BLUE CAMARO.

27:59.111 --> 28:01.714
THE SAME TYPE OF CAR
PARKED OUTSIDE OF OLENA'S

28:01.748 --> 28:02.815
THE NIGHT SHE DISAPPEARED.

28:02.849 --> 28:04.951
EXCUSE ME!

28:05.985 --> 28:07.720
HI, EVERYBODY!

28:07.754 --> 28:09.822
LISTEN, I...

28:09.856 --> 28:11.924
WAS BACKING UP
IN THE PARKING LOT,

28:11.958 --> 28:15.828
AND I KIND OF SORT OF HIT
A BLUE CAMARO.

28:15.862 --> 28:17.964
SO WHOSEVER CAR THAT IS,

28:17.997 --> 28:20.833
I WILL TOTALLY PAY FOR
THE DAMAGE, AND I AM SO SORRY.

28:20.867 --> 28:22.769
YEAH, THAT'S MY CAR.

28:25.071 --> 28:26.739
HOW BAD IS IT?

28:26.773 --> 28:28.741
IT'S PRETTY BAD.
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:28.775 --> 28:31.010
FBI.
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

28:31.043 --> 28:33.145
[ PATRONS MURMURING ]

28:37.083 --> 28:40.853
I WAS THERE,
BUT I DIDN'T KILL OLENA.

28:40.887 --> 28:42.889
I LOVED HER.

28:46.025 --> 28:49.028
I GOT A SIDE GIG
INSTALLING SATELLITE DISHES.

28:49.061 --> 28:50.963
IT PAYS FOR MY MUSIC.

28:50.997 --> 28:54.066
A COUPLE MONTHS AGO, I PUT IN
A DISH AT OLENA'S HOUSE.

28:54.100 --> 28:56.769
SHE WAS LONELY.

28:56.803 --> 28:59.005
WE TALKED AND STARTED
SEEING EACH OTHER.

28:59.038 --> 29:00.873
SHE WOULD NEVER
SPEND THE NIGHT.

29:00.907 --> 29:02.975
SHE ALWAYS HAD TO GET HOME
BEFORE FRANK DID.

29:03.009 --> 29:04.977
SHE TOLD ME THAT SHE WAS
GONNA LEAVE HIM.

29:05.011 --> 29:07.780
WELL, MAYBE YOU REALIZED
THAT WAS NEVER GONNA HAPPEN,

29:07.814 --> 29:10.783
SO YOU GOT ANGRY
AND YOU KILLED HER.

29:10.817 --> 29:13.920
NO! NO, SHE WAS SUPPOSED TO
COME OVER AND NEVER SHOWED.

29:13.953 --> 29:16.022
SHE DIDN'T
PICK UP HER PHONE.

29:16.055 --> 29:18.991
I GOT SCARED THAT FRANK
MAYBE FOUND OUT ABOUT US
AND MAYBE HE HURT HER.

29:19.025 --> 29:20.159
I DROVE OVER.

29:20.192 --> 29:23.029
NO ONE ANSWERED THE DOOR,
SO I BROKE IN.

29:23.062 --> 29:26.165
BUT OLENA WASN'T THERE.

29:26.198 --> 29:28.034
AND THEN FRANK CAME IN.

29:28.067 --> 29:29.869
AND HE TURNED ON
THE LIGHTS.

29:29.902 --> 29:32.805
HE RUSHED ME, SO I GRABBED
A LAMP AND I HIT HIM.

29:32.839 --> 29:34.941
AND THEN
I GOT THE [BLEEP] OUT OF THERE.

29:34.974 --> 29:37.009
THAT'S A VERY COMPELLING
STORY, JAKE,

29:37.043 --> 29:39.011
EXCEPT IT DOESN'T EXPLAIN
ONE THING.

29:39.045 --> 29:41.080
HOW DOES JOLENE GREY
FIT IN?

29:41.113 --> 29:42.915
WHO?

29:42.949 --> 29:44.817
SUPER-HOTTIE,

29:44.851 --> 29:46.018
BLACK HAIR.

29:46.052 --> 29:47.186
COMES TO SEE YOU PLAY

29:47.219 --> 29:49.822
EVERY THURSDAY NIGHT
AT THE RED RABBLE.

29:49.856 --> 29:51.190
LOTS OF PEOPLE
COME TO HEAR US.

29:51.223 --> 29:53.192
ARE YOU THINKING
WHAT I'M THINKING?

29:53.225 --> 29:55.027
EXCEPT JOLENE
WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR

29:55.061 --> 29:56.829
WITH OLENA'S HUSBAND,
FRANK.

29:56.863 --> 29:58.965
NOW, IT CANNOT JUST BE
A COINCIDENCE.

29:58.998 --> 30:01.167
I BET YOU KNOW
WHO THE MOLE IS NOW.

30:03.135 --> 30:05.838
I DON'T KNOW
ANY JOLENE GREY.

30:05.872 --> 30:08.074
ACTUALLY, YOU DO.

30:08.107 --> 30:10.242
YOU -- YOU KNOW HER
INTIMATELY.

30:18.284 --> 30:21.988
Kate: MR. PRENTICE, CAN YOU
HELP US I.D. THIS WOMAN?

30:23.022 --> 30:24.156
Frank: NO. WHO IS SHE?

30:24.190 --> 30:26.258
THERE ANYTHING ABOUT HER
THAT'S FAMILIAR TO YOU?

30:26.292 --> 30:27.927
HER HAIR, MAYBE?

30:27.960 --> 30:29.228
NO.
WHY -- WHY WOULD I --

30:29.261 --> 30:33.032
YOU'VE BEEN HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH THIS WOMAN FOR MONTHS.

30:34.166 --> 30:36.002
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S [BLEEP]

30:36.035 --> 30:38.170
WELL, MAYBE HER NAME WILL
RING A BELL -- JOLENE GREY?

30:40.206 --> 30:41.307
NO. I-I DON'T KNOW.

30:41.340 --> 30:43.242
YOU'VE BEEN PAYING OFF
HER CREDIT CARDS.

30:43.275 --> 30:44.276
WE HAVE THE RECORDS.

30:49.215 --> 30:53.185
OKAY, SO I BOUGHT JOLENE
SOME NICE STUFF.

30:53.219 --> 30:56.255
WHAT? ARE YOU SAYING
SOMEBODY KILLED HER?

30:56.288 --> 31:00.026
ACTUALLY, THE REAL JOLENE GREY
IS VERY MUCH ALIVE.

31:00.059 --> 31:03.195
YEAH, SHE LIVES OUT
IN THE 'BURBS WITH HER FAMILY.

31:03.229 --> 31:05.131
THIS WOMAN
STOLE HER IDENTITY.

31:05.164 --> 31:07.199
SHE WORE A WIG TO MAKE SURE
YOU WOULDN'T RECOGNIZE HER --

31:07.233 --> 31:08.367
VERY MUCH LIKE THIS ONE.

31:10.002 --> 31:13.172
I'LL BET
YOU RECOGNIZE HER NOW.

31:13.205 --> 31:16.208
YOU PUT A WIG ON A CORPSE?
WHAT KIND OF SICK --

31:16.242 --> 31:18.110
THAT'S OLENA.

31:18.144 --> 31:21.147
YOU WERE HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH YOUR OWN WIFE, FRANK.

31:23.015 --> 31:24.216
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

31:24.250 --> 31:26.118
ACTUALLY, IT IS.

31:26.152 --> 31:29.021
OLENA MUST HAVE FIGURED OUT OVER
TIME THAT YOU WERE FACE-BLIND,

31:29.055 --> 31:31.991
SO SHE STOLE ANOTHER WOMAN'S
IDENTITY AND SEDUCED YOU.

31:32.024 --> 31:34.126
SHE WAS PRACTICALLY
A PRISONER IN YOUR HOME,

31:34.160 --> 31:36.228
SO SHE USED YOUR CONDITION
AGAINST YOU

31:36.262 --> 31:38.064
TO BILK YOU
FOR CASH, JEWELS.

31:38.097 --> 31:41.067
I THINK SHE WAS PROBABLY
TRYING TO SAVE UP ENOUGH MONEY

31:41.100 --> 31:43.302
TO GET AWAY FROM YOU,
BUT, UH, TURNS OUT

31:43.335 --> 31:46.105
YOU WEREN'T THE ONLY ONE
SHE WAS SCREWING.

31:47.239 --> 31:49.008
WHAT?

31:49.041 --> 31:50.342
YEAH, TURNS OUT
WHILE YOU WERE AWAY AT WORK,

31:50.376 --> 31:53.179
SHE WAS BANGING THE GUY WHO
INSTALLED YOUR SATELLITE DISH.

31:53.212 --> 31:56.082
HE TOLD US ALL ABOUT IT.

31:56.115 --> 31:57.316
THAT [BLEEP]

31:57.349 --> 31:59.351
YOU CAN'T REALLY BLAME HER
FOR WANTING A BOY TOY

31:59.385 --> 32:01.320
WHEN SHE WAS
HAVING TO SLEEP WITH YOU

32:01.353 --> 32:03.055
AS HERSELF
AND AS JOLENE.

32:03.089 --> 32:04.356
OLENA WAS NEVER
ABDUCTED, FRANK.

32:04.390 --> 32:07.193
THE REASON NOBODY COULD FIND HER
IS THAT WHEN YOU KILLED

32:07.226 --> 32:09.228
THE WOMAN YOU THOUGHT
WAS YOUR MISTRESS,

32:09.261 --> 32:11.230
YOU'D REALLY JUST MURDERED
YOUR OWN WIFE.

32:11.263 --> 32:13.032
T-THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

32:13.065 --> 32:15.101
HOTEL DESK CLERK
PUTS YOU IN THE SAME ROOM AS HER

32:15.134 --> 32:16.268
ON THE DAY OF THE MURDER.

32:25.311 --> 32:27.146
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

32:28.414 --> 32:30.149
I NEVER MEANT TO KILL HER.

32:31.150 --> 32:35.087
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED.
MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU.

32:37.256 --> 32:39.125
I TRIED TO END IT
WITH HER.

32:39.158 --> 32:41.093
SHE -- SHE WAS
BLEEDING ME DRY.

32:41.127 --> 32:43.095
I COULDN'T
AFFORD HER ANYMORE.

32:43.129 --> 32:45.364
I TOLD HER I WAS GONNA
NEED THE JEWELRY BACK
TO PAY OFF YURI,

32:45.397 --> 32:47.333
OR ELSE
HE WAS GONNA TAKE OLENA.

32:48.400 --> 32:51.370
BUT JOLENE WOULDN'T LISTEN,
YOU KNOW?

32:51.403 --> 32:54.373
NO. SAID SHE WAS NOTHING
WITHOUT ME.

32:54.406 --> 32:57.143
THEN SHE
STARTED TO HIT ME.

32:57.176 --> 32:59.111
I LOST IT.

33:05.117 --> 33:07.186
WHAT ABOUT THE BODY?

33:08.420 --> 33:10.389
I WAITED
UNTIL AFTER DARK,

33:10.422 --> 33:12.258
TOOK HER DOWN IN
THE MAINTENANCE ELEVATOR,

33:12.291 --> 33:13.459
AND TOSSED HER
IN THE DUMPSTER.

33:16.462 --> 33:19.365
IT'S TOO BAD WE CAN'T CHARGE YOU
WITH TWO MURDERS.

33:22.501 --> 33:24.103
Paul: DANIEL.

33:24.136 --> 33:25.104
OH, HEY, PAUL.

33:25.137 --> 33:27.139
DON'T "HEY, PAUL" ME.

33:27.173 --> 33:29.108
YOU KNOW, YOU REALLY BLEW IT
WITH HATHAWAY.

33:29.141 --> 33:31.277
WHY WOULD YOU WANT A FRAUD LIKE
THAT ON THE FACULTY, ANYWAY?

33:31.310 --> 33:33.112
THAT FRAUD
IS AN ACADEMIC SUPERSTAR.

33:33.145 --> 33:35.114
EVERYBODY WANTS HIM --
HARVARD, NORTHWESTERN --

33:35.147 --> 33:37.416
BUT I AM GONNA GET HIM,
AND YOU'RE GONNA HELP ME DO IT.

33:37.449 --> 33:38.450
HERE.

33:38.484 --> 33:40.186
CUBS TICKETS.

33:40.219 --> 33:41.453
NOW, YOU'RE GONNA APOLOGIZE
TO HATHAWAY,

33:41.487 --> 33:43.422
AND YOU'RE GONNA INVITE HIM
TO TONIGHT'S GAME

33:43.455 --> 33:45.157
AS A PEACE OFFERING.

33:45.191 --> 33:47.326
COME ON, DANIEL.ILL.

33:47.359 --> 33:49.161
I REALLY NEED YOU
TO DO THIS FOR ME.

33:54.466 --> 33:57.169
COME ON, MAN.
YOU LOVE THE CUBBIES.

33:58.504 --> 34:00.439
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:00.472 --> 34:01.473
DANIEL.

34:02.474 --> 34:04.176
[ SIGHS ] KATE.

34:04.210 --> 34:05.477
HI.
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

34:05.511 --> 34:08.480
FRANK PRENTICE IS TAKING A PLEA
AND COOPERATING AGAINST YURI.

34:08.514 --> 34:10.216
THAT'S GREAT.

34:10.249 --> 34:12.218
AND IF WE CAN GET YURI
TO ROLL ON TUPELOV,

34:12.251 --> 34:15.454
THEN WE'LL HAVE THE UKRAINIANS
AND OLENA'S KILLER IN ONE SHOT.

34:15.487 --> 34:17.456
DO YOU LIKE BASEBALL?

34:17.489 --> 34:18.457
YEAH, SURE.

34:18.490 --> 34:20.192
I MEAN, WHO DOESN'T LIKE

34:20.226 --> 34:22.294
A COLD BEER AND A HOT DOG
AT A BALLGAME, RIGHT?

34:22.328 --> 34:25.197
WELL, I-I, UH,
JUST HAPPEN TO HAVE

34:25.231 --> 34:28.434
TWO, UH, TWO TICKETS
TO THE CUBS GAME TONIGHT.

34:29.435 --> 34:31.570
THAT SOUNDS GREAT.
WHAT TIME?

34:34.273 --> 34:35.507
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

34:37.509 --> 34:39.445
[ OVERLAPPING VOICES ]

34:44.216 --> 34:45.384
HAVE FUN.

34:46.552 --> 34:49.355
WAIT, YOU'RE NOT GOING?

34:49.388 --> 34:50.456
UH, NO.

34:51.523 --> 34:53.392
CROWDS DRIVE ME CRAZY.

34:53.425 --> 34:54.426
AH.

34:56.228 --> 34:57.263
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:57.296 --> 34:58.597
THANKS.

34:59.598 --> 35:01.267
ARE YOU STALKING ME?

35:01.300 --> 35:02.268
OH, MY GOD.

35:02.301 --> 35:03.435
[ BOTH CHUCKLHI.

35:03.469 --> 35:05.537
I COULD ASK YOU
THE SAME QUESTION.

35:05.571 --> 35:07.373
LAST CHANCE
TO BUY ME THAT DRINK.

35:07.406 --> 35:08.407
I LEAVE TOWN TOMORROW.

35:08.440 --> 35:11.243
UH, YOU KNOW, I'M SORRY.

35:11.277 --> 35:13.212
I DON'T THINK I CAN.
I HAVE PLANS.

35:13.245 --> 35:14.580
BUT TRAVEL SAFE.

35:18.417 --> 35:20.419
ACTUALLY, UM...

35:23.255 --> 35:24.423
DO YOU LIKE BASEBALL?

35:27.326 --> 35:29.395
Natalie:
WHY DIDN'T YOU TAKE KATE?

35:31.430 --> 35:34.266
BECAUSE I'D RATHER
WATCH IT ON TV...

35:34.300 --> 35:35.367
WITH YOU.

35:35.401 --> 35:37.503
SOMETHING'S BOTHERING YOU.

35:39.271 --> 35:40.572
IT'S OLENA.

35:40.606 --> 35:42.541
I JUST --
I CAN'T FIGURE OUT

35:42.574 --> 35:45.377
HOW A YOUNG GIRL
WHO BARELY SPOKE ENGLISH

35:45.411 --> 35:47.479
PULLED OFF
SUCH A COMPLICATED SCAM.

35:47.513 --> 35:49.481
I GUESS
SHE HAD EVERYONE FOOLED.

35:49.515 --> 35:51.450
Man: FOUL BALL
DOWN THE THIRD-BASE SIDE.

35:51.483 --> 35:53.419
OUT OF PLAY.

35:53.452 --> 35:55.487
WHOA.
GREAT CATCH BY THAT FAN.

35:55.521 --> 35:58.490
OH, I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

35:58.524 --> 36:00.292
SHE TOOK THAT [BLEEP]

36:00.326 --> 36:01.493
AND HE CATCHES
A FOUL BALL.

36:01.527 --> 36:03.329
YOU KNOW HOW MANY GAMES
I WENT TO AS A KID,

36:03.362 --> 36:05.431
AND I NEVER ONCE
CAUGHT A FOUL BALL?

36:05.464 --> 36:08.334
DANIEL, YOU HAVE NO ONE
TO BLAME BUT YOURSELF.

36:08.367 --> 36:09.468
THAT COULD HAVE BEEN YOU.

36:09.501 --> 36:11.637
BUT INSTEAD,
YOU LET HIM TAKE YOUR PLACE.

36:15.674 --> 36:17.676
SHE TOOK HER PLACE.

36:20.512 --> 36:22.448
THERE'S ANOTHER MOLE.

36:22.481 --> 36:25.284
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

36:25.317 --> 36:26.285
WHO ARE YOU CALLING?

36:26.318 --> 36:27.419
KATE.

36:27.453 --> 36:28.587
ARE YOU TRYING TO RUIN
HER DATE?

36:28.620 --> 36:30.456
[ BUTTONS CLICKING ]

36:30.489 --> 36:33.492
I'M GONNA TELL HER
OLENA ISN'T DEAD.

36:41.867 --> 36:43.735
YOU TAKING EVERYTHING?

36:43.769 --> 36:45.937
MRS. PRENTICE IS DEAD, AND
MR. PRENTICE GO TO JAIL, SO --

36:45.971 --> 36:47.973
IT'S OKAY. NO ONE'S
ACCUSING YOU OF STEALING.

36:48.006 --> 36:50.041
IT ALL BELONGS TO YOU,
ANYWAY, DOESN'T IT...

36:51.877 --> 36:52.911
...OLENA?

36:53.912 --> 36:55.681
LISTEN,
FRANK PRENTICE IS A PIG.

36:55.714 --> 36:57.816
WE DON'T BLAME YOU
FOR WANTING TO MAKE HIM PAY.

36:57.849 --> 37:00.886
WHAT WE COULDN'T FIGURE
OUT WAS HOW YOU DID
IT ALL ON YOUR OWN.

37:00.919 --> 37:02.854
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING --

37:02.888 --> 37:04.022
I REMEMBERED YOU MENTIONED

37:04.055 --> 37:06.024
A COUSIN THAT FRANK
DIDN'T LIKE -- PAULINA.

37:08.794 --> 37:12.831
EVER SINCE WE WERE LITTLE GIRLS
IN UKRAINE, PAULINA PROTECT ME.

37:12.864 --> 37:14.900
AND NOW SHE PROTECTED YOU
FROM FRANK.

37:16.935 --> 37:19.871
SHE MARRIED AMERICAN, TOO,
FIVE YEARS BEFORE,

37:19.905 --> 37:22.741
BUT SHE DIVORCE HIM,
STAY IN COUNTRY.

37:22.774 --> 37:25.711
I CALL HER,
ASK HER TO COME.

37:25.744 --> 37:27.713
IT WAS SO GOOD TO SEE HER.

37:27.746 --> 37:30.716
SHE STAYED FOR A FEW DAYS.

37:30.749 --> 37:34.720
BUT SOON WE NOTICE
SOMETHING STRANGE.

37:34.753 --> 37:38.757
MY HUSBAND SOMETIMES --
HE THINK PAULINA IS ME.

37:50.035 --> 37:53.739
WHEN NEXT TIME SHE COME
TO VISIT, HE NOT RECOGNIZE HER,

37:53.772 --> 37:55.073
EVEN THOUGH HE KNOW HER.

37:55.106 --> 37:57.743
THAT'S WHEN SHE REALIZED
HE WAS FACE-BLIND.

37:57.776 --> 37:59.911
AND SHE MAKE PLAN
TO GET HIS MONEY.

37:59.945 --> 38:04.082
BUT FIRST SHE NEED NEW NAME
SO HE DOESN'T GET SUSPICIOUS.

38:04.115 --> 38:08.954
SO SHE STEAL WALLET AT MALL,

38:08.987 --> 38:12.858
AND SHE MAKE HERSELF LOOK LIKE
WOMAN ON DRIVING LICENSE.

38:14.125 --> 38:18.129
HE'S NOT USED TO BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
PAYING ATTENTION TO HIM,

38:18.163 --> 38:24.035
SO HE GIVE HER MONEY, JEWELS,
ANYTHING SHE WANT.

38:24.069 --> 38:25.937
FOR ME, IT GET WORSE.

38:26.972 --> 38:28.907
I WANT TO RUN AWAY.

38:28.940 --> 38:32.978
BUT PAULINA SAY WE HAVE TO WAIT
UNTIL WE GET ALL FRANK'S MONEY

38:33.011 --> 38:36.782
AND THAT SHE HAVE NEW PLAN
TO PROTECT ME.

38:36.815 --> 38:41.853
I GIVE HER HAIRCUT, AND I GIVE
HER MY CLOTHES AND MY PERFUME.

38:42.954 --> 38:46.124
PAULINA IS STRONGER THAN ME.

38:46.157 --> 38:48.894
SHE MAKE FRANK
STOP HITTING HER...

38:50.095 --> 38:53.965
...AND SHE CONVINCE FRANK
TO HIRE UKRAINIAN MAID

38:53.999 --> 38:55.934
TO KEEP HER COMPANY.

38:55.967 --> 38:59.971
SO PAULINA
BECAME YOU AND JOLENE,

39:00.005 --> 39:01.840
AND YOU BECAME THE MAID.

39:01.873 --> 39:03.108
IT'S AN INGENIOUS PLAN.

39:03.141 --> 39:05.844
YOU ARE
GOING TO ARREST ME.

39:06.912 --> 39:08.146
YOU'RE AN ACCESSORY
TO FRAUD.

39:08.179 --> 39:10.816
THE U.S. ATTORNEY'S OFFICE
MIGHT WANT TO CHARGE YOU,

39:10.849 --> 39:12.818
BUT I'LL DO MY BEST
TO CONVINCE THEM

39:12.851 --> 39:15.086
THAT BEING MARRIED
TO AN ABUSIVE, CHEATING MURDERER

39:15.120 --> 39:17.022
WAS PROBABLY
PUNISHMENT ENOUGH.

39:20.058 --> 39:21.860
THANK YOU.

39:21.893 --> 39:25.130
BUT MY HUSBAND WILL FIND OUT
WHAT WE DID TO HIM,

39:25.163 --> 39:27.866
AND WHEN HE LEAVE PRISON,
HE WILL FIND ME,

39:27.899 --> 39:28.834
AND WITHOUT PAULINA --

39:28.867 --> 39:30.035
YOU WERE THREATENED

39:30.068 --> 39:32.170
BY A KNOWN ASSOCIATE
OF THE TUPELOV ORGANIZATION.

39:32.203 --> 39:33.972
I CAN MAKE
A PRETTY GOOD CASE

39:34.005 --> 39:35.907
THAT YOU BELONG
IN WITNESS PROTECTION.

39:35.941 --> 39:39.044
YOU'LL GET A FRESH START, OLENA.
NEW NAME, NEW LIFE.

39:42.213 --> 39:43.849
Paul: DANIEL!

39:43.882 --> 39:45.851
PAUL, LOOK,
I KNOW YOU'RE UPSET.

39:45.884 --> 39:46.918
UPSET? NO, NO, NO.

39:46.952 --> 39:49.054
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU SAID TO HATHAWAY,

39:49.087 --> 39:51.890
