HE IS IN LOVE WITH THIS TOWN.

39:51.923 --> 39:54.926
HE'S TAKING THE JOB.
YOU DID GOOD, BUDDY.

39:54.960 --> 39:59.865
Daniel: WALT WHITMAN WROTE,
"I CONTAIN MULTITUDES."

39:59.898 --> 40:02.000
